| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1683 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8e80cde2-8a6c-5bbf-a653-5128d07da7ae"
